scripts.git-pull-develop: git checkout develop && git pull origin master && git push origin develop
scripts.git-pull-beta-release: git checkout beta-release && git pull origin master && git push origin beta-release
scripts.git-pull-master: git checkout master && git pull origin master
scripts.git-pull-all: npm run git-pull-master && npm run git-pull-beta-release && npm run git-pull-develop
